jorgan (3.21) beta;

  * core: new MLP command 'round'
  * gui: allow sorting by type or name when selecting elements
  * gui: rearranging of console tabs is optional now
  * gui: double click on message in the Midi monitor to select the originating element
  * tools: RepeatSwitch supports duration   
  * sams: new property 'maximum' for SAMs element   

 -- Sven Meier <sven@meiers.net>  Mon, 02 Dec 2013 23:00:00 +0200

jorgan (3.20) stable;

  * core: store preferences specific to runtime-architecture
  * core: new element Synchronizing to synchronize continuous elements
  * core: optionally enumerate and cache Midi devices
  * core: if Rank#channel is empty, no message's channel is altered
  * cli: new command to monitor Midi input/output
  * gui: allow zoom less than 0.5, now 0.25 minimum 
  * gui: console tabs can no longer be rearranged/hidden   
  * exporter: preselect elements based on current selection
  * fluidsynth: tunings table with right-aligned headers and index on each row
  * installer: use 32bit program folder for 32bit jOrgan on 64bit system
  * package: keep virmidi from being loaded as first soundcard

 -- Sven Meier <sven@meiers.net>  Thu, 25 Nov 2013 23:00:00 +0200

jorgan (3.19) stable;

  * core: fixed bug when Regulator has no reference
  * core: Synchronizer action ACTIVATE now activates instead of set activate, action DEACTIVATE now deactivates instead of set deactive
  * core: Synchronizer new actions SET_ACTIVE and SET_DEACTIVE
  * fluidsynth: new bank offset
  * tools: new element RepeatSwitch
  * tools: new element ConnectionSwitch

 -- Sven Meier <sven@meiers.net>  Thu, 28 Feb 2013 23:00:00 +0200

